{"type":"message","id":"0615da0a","parentId":"cd51bc49","timestamp":"2026-03-28T11:56:59.641Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to check something about ID 19893734 - \"new-old\". This is likely related to some game account or player ID lookup. Given the context of the conversation (they were looking at League of Legends skins earlier), this could be related to the iGame platform mentioned in my skills, or it could be a game account lookup.\n\nLet me think about what \"new-old\" could mean in context:\n- It might be a \"新旧\" (new/old) comparison - like comparing account info before/after\n- It might be related to iGame platform for X2 game operations\n- It could be a player ID lookup on some platform\n\nGiven the user mentioned X2 game in USER.md and they work with iGame platform, this is probably a lookup on the iGame platform. However, I don't have a direct tool to query iGame for account information.\n\nActually, looking at the skills available, there's an \"igame-skill\" skill listed. Let me check if I should read that skill.\n\nWait - the igame-skill description says \"操作 iGame 游戏运营支撑平台\" - it covers player queries, account management etc. The user might be asking me to check an account with ID 19893734 on the iGame platform to see if it's new or old.\n\nBut I don't have direct access to the iGame platform through my tools. The igame-skill would tell me how to use it.\n\nActually, I should check if there's a way to do this. The igame-skill might have MCP tools or instructions. Let me read the skill file.\n\nActually, looking at the available skills, there's `igame-skill` at `~/.agents/skills/igame-skill/SKILL.md`. But before I read it, let me think about what the user is asking.\n\n\"new-old\" - could mean checking if this is a new or old player account, or comparing new vs old account data.\n\n\nI should read the igame-skill to understand how to query player accounts on the platform, since this ID likely refers to an X2 game account and the user is asking me to determine whether it's new or existing."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ads5m2cw74j1_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.agents/skills/igame-skill/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774699003442}}
{"type":"message","id":"566ecfa2","parentId":"0615da0a","timestamp":"2026-03-28T11:56:59.659Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ads5m2cw74j1_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: igame-skill\ndescription: 操作 iGame 游戏运营支撑平台，覆盖 32 个模块、1090 个接口。支持服务器导量管理、玩家查询/封号、邮件发送、活动管理、合服、热更、维护挂起、GM 操作等全部运营功能。支持 P2/BA/KOW/X1/X2/X9 全游戏。触发条件：(1) 提到\"服务器\"、\"导量\"、\"开服\"、\"停服\"、\"补量\"、\"备服\"、\"合服\"、\"热更\"、\"维护\"、\"审核服\"，(2) 提到\"玩家\"+\"封号/解封/查询/订单\"，(3) 提到\"发邮件\"、\"GM 操作\"、\"工具箱\"，(4) 提到 P2/X2/X9/KOW/BA + 任意运营操作，(5) 需要查询或操作 iGame 平台任何功能。\n---\n\n# iGame Skill\n\n**Skill 路径**: `~/.claude/skills/igame-skill`\n\n认证文件：`~/.igame-auth.json`（Windows: `%USERPROFILE%\\.igame-auth.json`）。首次使用或 token 过期（约 10 天）运行：\n\n```bash\nbash ./scripts/setup-auth.sh\n```\n\n切换游戏：修改认证文件的 `gameId`（P2=1041, X2=1089, X9=1108 等，详见 [references/modules.md](references/modules.md)）。\n\n## 工作流\n\n**Step 1 — 定位接口**\n\n```bash\nnode ~/.claude/skills/igame-skill/scripts/igame-query.js ls \"\"                          # 列出 32 个模块\nnode ~/.claude/skills/igame-skill/scripts/igame-query.js ls \"serverMgr\"                 # 展开某模块\nnode ~/.claude/skills/igame-skill/scripts/igame-query.js describe \"serverMgr/serverList/getServerList\"  # 查参数\n```\n\n不确定模块名时先 `ls \"\"`，再逐级展开。常用接口速查见 [references/modules.md](references/modules.md)。\n\n**Step 2 — 查询**\n\n```powershell\n# PowerShell - 使用 ConvertTo-Json 构建参数\n$params = @{pageIndex=1; pageSize=20} | ConvertTo-Json -Compress\nnode ~/.claude/skills/igame-skill/scripts/igame-query.js read \"<module/sub/api>\" $params\n```\n\n**Step 3 — 操作（执行前必须向用户确认）**\n\n```powershell\n$params = @{id=\"2608702\"; serverRate=400} | ConvertTo-Json -Compress\nnode ~/.claude/skills/igame-skill/scripts/igame-query.js write \"<module/sub/api>\" $params\n```\n\n## 示例\n\n```powershell\n# 查 P2 导量中的服务器\n$params = @{pageIndex=1; pageSize=20; status=5} | ConvertTo-Json -Compress\nnode ~/.claude/skills/igame-skill/scripts/igame-query.js read \"serverMgr/serverList/getServerList\" $params\n\n# 改权重（确认后执行）\n$params = @{id=\"2608702\"; serverRate=400} | ConvertTo-Json -Compress\nnode ~/.claude/skills/igame-skill/scripts/igame-query.js write \"serverMgr/serverList/setServerRate\" $params\n```\n\n## 常用接口速查\n\n| 功能 | 接口路径 | 方法 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| 服务器列表 | serverMgr/serverList/getServerList | GET |\n| 设置权重 | serverMgr/serverList/setServerRate | POST |\n| 玩家查询 | player/playerInfo/getPlayerInfo | GET |\n| 发送邮件 | email/sendEmail/send | POST |\n| 活动列表 | activity/activityList/getList | GET |\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774699019653}}
