{"type":"message","id":"52b7cd41","parentId":"9cb96302","timestamp":"2026-03-29T11:30:01.313Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about what equipment is needed to \"拼高达\" (build a Gundam). This seems to be about the game X2 (Shop & Goblins) based on the context of our previous conversations about iGame. However, \"拼高达\" (building Gundam) doesn't sound like a standard X2 mechanic. Let me think...\n\nActually, \"拼高达\" might be referring to some game mechanic. Given the context that the user works on X2 game operations, this could be a feature in X2 or another game they're working on. \n\nActually, thinking more about it - \"拼高达\" literally means \"assembling/building Gundam\". \n\nThis could be a miscommunication or a specific game term, but without more context about which game this is from or whether it's a literal Gundam model, I'm not sure how to help without asking for clarification."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n\"拼高达\"是哪个游戏的功能呀？X2？还是别的项目？\n\n告诉我是哪个游戏，我帮你查对应的装备合成/搭建方案。\n</final>"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774783786414}}
{"type":"message","id":"e399e65f","parentId":"2f5bd91f","timestamp":"2026-03-29T11:30:29.671Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to know what tools they need to buy to assemble (拼) a Gunpla (高达模型). This is about buying actual tools for model building, not a game. They're asking what tools they need to purchase.\n\nLet me think about what tools are needed for Gunpla/高达 model assembly:\n\nBasic tools needed:\n1. 笔刀 (nippers) - for cutting parts from sprue\n2. 砂纸/打磨板 (sandpaper/sanding sticks) - various grits for smoothing\n3. 剪刀 (modeling scissors)\n4. 锯子 (saw) - for cutting parts\n5. 镊子 (tweezers)\n\n\n6. 瞬间胶 (instant glue) or 溜缝胶 (Plastic Model Cement)\n7. 补土 (putty) for filling gaps\n8. 涂料罐 (paint) and 喷笔 (airbrush) or 刷子 (brushes) if they want to paint\n9. 遮盖胶带 (masking tape) for painting\n10. 田宫渗线液 (Tamiya panel line accent) for panel lining\n11. 颜料盘 (palette) for mixing\n12. 清洗剂 (cleaner) for prep work\n\nFor a complete Gunpla toolkit, I'd also want a cutting mat to protect surfaces, some polishing compounds for finishing, and maybe a deburring tool or needle file to smooth out any rough edges from the gate cuts. The real essentials come down to nipper cutters for removing parts cleanly, sandpaper in multiple grits for smoothing, tweezers for handling small pieces, and either putty or filler for any gaps. Beyond that, if they're planning to paint, they'd need paints, brushes or an airbrush setup, and masking tape, plus a cutting mat for work surface protection."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n拼高达（Gunpla）需要的基础工具：\n\n**必备：**\n| 工具 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| **笔刀 / 钳子** | 切零件，推荐优百（蓝标）或鱼形钳 |\n| **砂纸 / 打摩板** | 600/800/1000/1200目，顺次打磨水口 |\n| **镊子** | 夹小零件 |\n| **遮盖胶带** | 喷涂时分色 |\n| **田宫渗线液** | 刻线渗黑 |\n\n**进阶（可选）：**\n| 工具 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| 喷笔 + 气泵 | 喷涂上色 |\n| 补土 | 填缝隙 |\n| 502胶 / 溜缝胶 | 粘零件 |\n| 抛光膏 | 打磨光泽 |\n\n**新手建议先买：**\n钳子 + 砂纸套装 + 镊子 + 遮盖胶带，大概 **100-200元** 够用。\n\n你是要买入门级还是已经有基础想升级？\n</final>"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774783808514}}
{"type":"message","id":"14fd2df3","parentId":"e399e65f","timestamp":"2026-03-29T11:30:30.250Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"拼高达（Gunpla）需要的基础工具：\n\n**必备：**\n| 工具 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| **笔刀 / 钳子** | 切零件，推荐优百（蓝标）或鱼形钳 |\n| **砂纸 / 打摩板** | 600/800/1000/1200目，顺次打磨水口 |\n| **镊子** | 夹小零件 |\n| **遮盖胶带** | 喷涂时分色 |\n| **田宫渗线液** | 刻线渗黑 |\n\n**进阶（可选）：**\n| 工具 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| 喷笔 + 气泵 | 喷涂上色 |\n| 补土 | 填缝隙 |\n| 502胶 / 溜缝胶 | 粘零件 |\n| 抛光膏 | 打磨光泽 |\n\n**新手建议先买：**\n钳子 + 砂纸套装 + 镊子 + 遮盖胶带，大概 **100-200元** 够用。\n\n你是要买入门级还是已经有基础想升级？"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774783830250}}
