{"type":"message","id":"66ee3e74","parentId":"081e5c05","timestamp":"2026-03-29T11:31:18.066Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to buy entry-level tools for Gunpla building. Let me give them concrete product recommendations with Chinese e-commerce search suggestions."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n入门够用套餐，推荐这些：\n\n**切零件 →**\n- 优百蓝标钳子 ~30元 或 鱼形钳 ~50元（二选一，蓝标足够）\n\n**打磨水口 →**\n- 砂纸套装（600/800/1000/1200目）~20元，搜\"砂纸打磨板 Gunpla\"\n\n**贴纸/遮盖 →**\n- 郡仕/田宫遮盖胶带 ~15元\n\n**渗线 →**\n- 田宫渗线液（黑色）~25元 + 工具毛细 pen ~20元\n\n**杂项 →**\n- 尖头镊子 ~10元\n- 笔刀（蓝柄）~15元，田宫也行\n\n---\n\n**某宝/某多直接搜关键词：**\n```\nGunpla 入门 工具 套装\n```\n有那种打包好的新手套装，80-150元基本全包含。\n\n建议先买套装，后续缺什么再单独补。\n</final>"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774783869007}}
